item.title: Prayer bpn13044 in Kube
item.description: Yomuhuc zêʒua. O Kewu. Kewu na orucna asacmararaŋ ganêŋ qezericna orucna hiabia waŋŋu. Zêma sêwina qezericna guac ackoazêc hêla nonac sêcgêma hemac. Imi hia. Geŋgaoc kekec hiawac maŋgia wandac zaŋ. (Source category: Ewa Niŋ Gêsiac Ac Mosoc) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 13044)
